SE demo -Project Structure


Home page
		-> This will show all posts of all users


Top Menu Bar
	Home Icon
		-> When we click on it , it has redirect on the top of the home page.

  	Group Icon 
		|-> We have to create a friends list when  we click on the group icon on the Top menu.
		|-> When we click on each friend in the list , it should display the individual details. 


Left Menu Bar
	Profile Icon
		-> When we click on it , it has show the profile of the current user

  	allPosts Icon 
		|-> Show the posts written by current user.	
	Events Icon
		|-> It will show all the details about the  events of the current user.

  Posting
	-> User can posts/write on the home page.
	->  User can read the posts.
	-> User can comment on posts.

Project Structure

	|-> Model Clases

		-> Posting    ( -> read 
			     		-> write
			     		-> comment Optional
					)
		-> left menu ( -> Profile 
			        	-> All posts 
			        	-> Events
					)

		-> Top menu ( -> home,
				 	-> Friends
					)
One-To-Many Association
	|-> ( User - Friend
			  - Post 
	       )
	



Buttons - 
   Home
	|-> Create Posts buttons

	|-> Edit Posts buttons
	|-> Delete Posts buttons

      Left menu bar
	|-> Profile icon
	|-> Events icon
	|-> All Current User Posts icon

      Top menu bar
	|-> home icon
	|-> friends Group icon


   Database

	1.TMBar
  	->Friend (list)
		* Friend_name : “Text_attribute”
			|-> Friend Individual details
				* Friend_name : “Text_attribute”
				*Friend_DOB : integer_attribute
				*email_id 	: “Text_attribute”
	2.LMBar
		|->Profile
			*Current_user_name : “text_attribute”
			*Current_user_DOB : integer_attribute
			*Current_user_email-id: “text-attribute”
			*Current_user_image: image
		|->Posts
			*Tile : “Text_attribute”
			* description : “Text_attribute”
		|->Events
			Display - “No current Events”

	3.Home_timeline
		|->Posts
			*Tile : “Text_attribute”
			* description : “Text_attribute”

		
		





